name: Lush swamp of Life
description:
(ZOOM IN PLS!) Made this one to cope with Covid-19's quarantine and my dark emotions. Life's drive to strive no matter the circumstances made me draw this one in order to expell dark emotions, heavy energies and express clumped up shit inside my heart and mind. Even the wretched parts of us, once recognized, can be admired. Spirituality is key to life itself. 

Traditional illustration ade with: 

- Various mm's nankin pen
- Markers
- A3 180gsm canson paper
